        <p style="margin-bottom: -0.8rem;"><span style="color: #da96ab;" class="text-Rounded700">色混ぜ</span><span class="panel-tool-button" style="cursor: default; color: black; display: inline-flex;"><i class="bi bi-droplet-half"></i></span>：
